ZH:汽车驶近停车场的时候，要注意周围的行人。
EN: When the car approaches the parking lot, pay attention to the pedestrians around.

ZH:他看到火车驶近，赶紧跑过去。
EN: He saw the train approaching and quickly ran over.

ZH:船只驶近海岸线时，必须严格遵守导航规则。
EN: When ships approach the coastline, they must strictly follow the navigation rules.

ZH:我们驶近飞往目的地的最后阶段。
EN: We are approaching the final stage of our journey to the destination.

